{"tid":2413813,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"依家係咪買外賣唔洗scan安心同填資料？","createTime":"2021-02-19T03:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-19T04:32:21.000Z","uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1d1a409566803f05c6b0e82c135f849a3733a305","tid":2413813,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"好亂吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4660702bd44b9f3acb12b575c00ac11b7a48f4b5","tid":2413813,"uid":306343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d1a409566803f05c6b0e82c135f849a3733a305","tid":2413813,"uid":254813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"好亂吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T04:32:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/18/P2021021800786.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F18%2FP2021021800786.htm&d=ffZD4KHswvQdDnqC%2BKe69EPclXdXKQfB%2FlJdEd6ZkMI%3D&h=a364af55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/18/P2021021800786.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n「考慮到在餐飲處所購買外賣的顧客不會脫下口罩，而且逗留時間比較短，因此純粹惠顧外賣的顧客（或為他們提取外賣的速遞員）不掃瞄「安心出行」場所二維碼是可以接受的。儘管並非指示要求，為保護自己、家人及朋友和協助疫情受控，我們鼓勵顧客掃瞄「安心出行」場所二維碼。」"}]}